SubjectOrder Repealing the Minimizing the Risk of Exposure to Ebola Virus Disease in Canada Order (No.4)
PrecisOrder Repealing the MINIMIZING THE RISK OF EXPOSURE TO EBOLA VIRUS DISEASE IN CANADA ORDER (NO.4) in order to lift the enhanced public health measures that currently apply to travellers who have visited Guinea within 21 days of entering Canada.
